name: Delicious Crispy Roast
desc: Large chunks of roasted meat. The moment it comes out of the oven, the rich, meaty aroma fills your soul. No wonder so many people from Nod-Krai say this roasted meat is like the warm sun when the cold falls and the biting winds blow.

value.text: Increases all party members' ATK by 228 for 300s. In Co-Op Mode, this effect only applies to your own character(s).
